Frequently Asked Questions
Are the courses beginner-friendly?

Yes. We offer programs for beginners as well as learners with prior technical experience.

Do the courses include practical projects?

Yes. Hands-on projects are integrated into the learning experience.

What technologies are covered?

Depending on the program, learners work with technologies such as Java, Python, Flutter, Docker, Kubernetes, Terraform, MongoDB, Firebase, and more.

Will I receive a certificate?

Yes. Certificates are provided upon successful completion of eligible programs.

Who are these programs designed for?

Students, professionals, and individuals looking to build or advance their technology skills.

